<table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=10>
<tr><td bgcolor="#363636">
<a name="broom_of_trilon"></a>
<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Broom of Trilon</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Skill: <a href="/weapons/1h_blunt.shtml">1H Blunt</a><BR>
Damage per second - 5.20<BR>
Damage 6 - Delay 25<BR>
Weight: 3.5 - DEF, ERU, GNM, HIE, HUM<BR>
Classes: <a href="/magician/weapons/1h_blunt.shtml">MAG</a><BR>
Effect: <a href="http://www.maximumeq.com/spells/individual/reclaim_energy.shtml?spellID=346">Reclaim Energy</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
(AGI +3) (INT +2) </font>
<BR>
Obtained through the <a href="/quests/broom_of_trilon.shtml?questID=115">Broom of Trilon</a> quest<BR>
Must be equipped to obtain a more powerful pet when summoning.<BR>

</td></tr>
