<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Anyka</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-01-26 11:22:32</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Correct.  The quest item broom drops frequently from the alligators in Cazic Thule and can be traded.  If you are doing the quest, just camp the green pool in Cazic for a few hours, you'll get all four.<BR>
<BR>
The focus item Broom is no drop -- you must do the quest itself.  Both frost and fire giant toes (and possibly others) drop from seafuries in OOT.  You can almost always find the toes for free from higher-level PCs.  The third items drop from greenies, i.e. scales from sirens in OOT and fire drakes in Lava.  The only reallyhard thing in this quest is the jewels, they are expensive and I think it cost me 500pp to get all four.<BR>
<BR>
Now a question -- how do these rank for melee weapons?  And what is "reclaim energy" and how does it work?  Is this a proc or do you right click broom to kill pet?</font></td></tr></table>
<BR>
