<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Can someone please post the correct info on this item.  I've heard and read from several different sources, including Everlore, that the broom is only the focus for casting the Air Elemental and that the Shovel is for the Earth Elemental and the torch is for the Fire Elemental and no mention is made for the Water Elemental.  From reading the comments from above, you get the impression that the broom is the sole item that you would need.  Who in the Temple gives this quest anyway?  I talked with Joyce in the Temple and she gives the quest for the Robes of the Element, The Clay Bracelet, The Earthen Boots and The Circlet of Mist.  I would really like to know the source of this quest, because it may be different on different servers.  Thanks.</font></td></tr></table>
